00:13:34.260 --> 00:13:40.780
And then I guess for me, I look at that and I go, I understand that that works for some people.

00:13:40.780 --> 00:13:44.560
But for me, I need to be inspired to write.

00:13:44.980 --> 00:13:46.980
And so I don't write when I'm not inspired.

00:13:46.980 --> 00:13:52.960
And if I'm working with somebody, I can't manage them.

00:13:52.960 --> 00:13:57.480
I can't like say you have to do this or that.

00:13:57.480 --> 00:14:07.300
