00:14:23.540 --> 00:14:28.800
And the third thing, and there might have been a fourth one that I can't remember right now.

00:14:28.800 --> 00:14:34.300
But the third thing is if the book fails, you walk away from it.

00:14:34.300 --> 00:14:36.920
Nobody owns anything about it.

00:14:37.600 --> 00:14:41.380
