00:15:39.580 --> 00:15:42.820
But capturing that inspiration is really important to me.

00:15:42.820 --> 00:15:45.840
And I can see how it's a tough balance with a co-author.

00:15:45.840 --> 00:15:54.220
Well, the one thing I wanted to point out was that I often see the people who say, oh, you have to do, you know, you have to work from 8 until noon every day.

00:15:54.220 --> 00:15:57.020
They're the ones who talk about it.

