Yeah.

00:20:53.460 --> 00:20:54.420
That's pretty intense.

00:20:54.420 --> 00:20:55.660
And this is a big bet, right?

00:20:55.660 --> 00:20:57.480
Every one of you has written the book.

00:20:57.480 --> 00:20:58.720
You know, you said nine months.

00:20:58.720 --> 00:21:00.380
Brian said a year.

00:21:00.540 --> 00:21:02.660
Like, that is a big project.

00:21:02.660 --> 00:21:06.360
And you don't really get that much feedback until you ship it.

00:21:06.360 --> 00:21:08.300
Catherine, you want to speak to that?

00:21:08.300 --> 00:21:10.840
Like, how did you think about that and handle it?

00:21:10.840 --> 00:21:19.780
