00:21:20.100 --> 00:21:24.600
So books were kind of like a mornings, nights, weekends.

00:21:24.600 --> 00:21:29.940
I have a very compassionate partner who would refill my coffee.

00:21:29.940 --> 00:21:36.800
And yeah, it was definitely something that was more of like a passion time.

00:21:36.800 --> 00:21:46.620
