00:23:27.360 --> 00:23:31.020
And the difference between half a million and $50,000 seems to me really, really significant.

00:23:31.020 --> 00:23:48.100
But all the benefits of you, you are all talking about of, say, having an editor, having the support, this whole success story that they had was predicated upon them having a very large following on their blog and around their sort of company or anyway.

00:23:48.100 --> 00:23:53.580
So I know some of you have self-published and some of you have gone through the traditional route.

00:23:53.580 --> 00:23:56.640
Maybe, Brian, do you want to take that first?

00:23:57.180 --> 00:23:58.440
Did you think about self-publishing?

00:23:58.440 --> 00:23:59.760
What are your thoughts on that?

00:23:59.760 --> 00:24:11.620
