00:33:14.680 --> 00:33:18.380
And then on the other hand, you can output HTML.

00:33:18.380 --> 00:33:22.080
You can output LaTeX and then compile that to a PDF.

00:33:22.460 --> 00:33:30.180
So that was, like, a central tool that I used where I could feed in my source files and then have all the different output formats that I needed generated.

00:33:30.180 --> 00:33:35.500
